  "detailed_description": "\"The PIGGY universe expands with PIGGY: HUNT, a multiplayer adventure where survivors team up to escape the wrath of the Infected, the monstrosity trying to hunt them down.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survivors</h2>Survivors complete tasks, solve puzzles, find and use tools to help one another survive and escape! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702320/extras/eeff5e14d37de5d694a89a9545eb2e89.poster.avif?t=1738964300\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702320/extras/eeff5e14d37de5d694a89a9545eb2e89.webm?t=1738964300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702320/extras/eeff5e14d37de5d694a89a9545eb2e89.mp4?t=1738964300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Infected</h2>Infected use traps and all of your senses to hunt down the Survivors! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702320/extras/c6af175b4963fa79e61b9b0bf8a565fe.poster.avif?t=1738964300\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702320/extras/c6af175b4963fa79e61b9b0bf8a565fe.webm?t=1738964300\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702320/extras/c6af175b4963fa79e61b9b0bf8a565fe.mp4?t=1738964300\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features: <br>• Fast-paced fun for up to 6 players; more players available with custom-game mode! <br>• Highly customizable characters, weapons, and items. <br>• Use custom-game mode to create endless playable options. <br>• 3 House maps to play, each with different mechanics to win.<br>• Officially licensed game from MiniToon.",
